msgstr "Abonamentul tău s-a încheiat, dar <0/> rămâne activ până la <1>{graceDate}</1>. Reabonează-te înainte de această dată pentru a-ți păstra istoricul de abonat."

#. Nagbar body shown while a premium subscription is in its grace period. {premiumProductName} is the premium product name and {formattedGraceDate} is already localized.
#: src/features/app/components/layout/app_layout/nagbars/PremiumGracePeriodNagbar.tsx:22
msgid "Your subscription failed to renew, but you still have access to {premiumProductName} perks until {formattedGraceDate}. Take action now or you'll lose all perks."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău nu a putut fi reînnoit, dar ai în continuare acces la beneficiile {premiumProductName} până la data de {formattedGraceDate}. Acționează acum sau vei pierde toate beneficiile."

#. Body text in the Plutonium subscription actions. Keep the tone plain and specific.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:44
msgid "Your subscription has been reactivated."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău a fost reactivat."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is set to cancel at the end of the billing period.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:20
msgid "Your subscription has been set to cancel at the end of your billing period."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău a fost setat să se anuleze la sfârșitul perioadei de facturare."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is switched from yearly to monthly billing.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:60
msgid "Your subscription has been switched to monthly billing."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău a fost trecut la facturarea lunară."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is switched from monthly to yearly billing.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:56
msgid "Your subscription has been switched to yearly billing."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău a fost comutat la facturarea anuală."

#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/SubscriptionCard.tsx:435
msgid "Your subscription is active but perks are temporarily paused."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău este activ, dar beneficiile sunt întrerupte temporar."

#. Body of the error modal shown when a subscription is already scheduled to cancel.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/utils/PremiumActionErrorModal.tsx:32
msgid "Your subscription is already set to cancel at the end of your billing period."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău este deja setat să se anuleze la sfârșitul perioadei de facturare."

#. Body of the error modal shown when reactivation is attempted but the subscription is not cancelling.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/utils/PremiumActionErrorModal.tsx:40
msgid "Your subscription isn't set to cancel, so there's nothing to reactivate."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău nu este setat pentru anulare, așa că nu este nimic de reactivat."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is scheduled to switch to monthly billing.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:68
msgid "Your subscription will switch to monthly billing at the next renewal."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău va trece la facturarea lunară la următoarea reînnoire."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is scheduled to switch to yearly billing.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:64
msgid "Your subscription will switch to yearly billing at the next renewal."
msgstr "Abonamentul tău va trece la facturarea anuală la următoarea reînnoire."

#. Body of the error modal shown when a theme CSS exceeds the maximum shareable size.
#: src/features/theme/components/modals/ShareThemeModal.tsx:58
msgid "Your theme CSS is too large to share. Trim it down and try again."
msgstr "CSS-ul temei tale este prea mare pentru a fi partajat. Redu-l și încearcă din nou."

#. Field label on the details step of the DSA report form. Optional Fluxer username of the reporter so staff can follow up.
